Package: SERO
Title: Spatial Emergency Response Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Prince Oppong Boakye <prynx44@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Prince Oppong Boakye <prynx44@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Prince", "Oppong Boakye", email = "prynx44@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Spatial emergency response optimization.
    Identifies accident hotspots using point pattern analysis, computes optimal 
    emergency service locations using 6 multi-criteria analysis criteria, and 
    calculates fastest routes to accident scenes. Uses R-spatial best practices 
    with sf, ggplot2, and spatstat. Focuses exclusively on built-in data from 
    inst/gpkg folder.
